#Basic Techniques
# Ability Name			Unique Key					SORTKEY					Category of Ability		Type								Description																																																																																				Source Page
Basic / Attack			KEY:MA_OS ~ Attack			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_A	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerBasic	DESC:You get a +1 bonus on rolls to Attack, Throw, Grapple, and Trip opponents.																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.81
Basic / Defenses			KEY:MA_OS ~ Defenses			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_A	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerBasic	DESC:You gain +1 bonus to AC when you are un- or lightly armored.																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.81
Basic / Power			KEY:MA_OS ~ Power				SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_A	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerBasic	DESC:Increase your unarmed damage by +1 or increase your weapon die type by 1 step, up to a d12 maximum. Weapons that cause multiple dice of damage increase them independently.																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.81
Basic / Strike			KEY:MA_OS ~ Strike			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_A	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerBasic	DESC:You may deal lethal or nonlethal damage at will without penalty. Your base damage is at least 1d4. This may only be taken once.																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.81
Basic / Synergy			KEY:MA_OS ~ Synergy			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_A	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerBasic	DESC:You gain +2 on any related skill. Each time this is taken it applies to a different skill. Common synergies include Tumble, Heal, and Move Silently, but others are possible.																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.81
Basic / Toughness			KEY:MA_OS ~ Toughness			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_A	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerBasic	DESC:You gain DR 1/-. This stacks with itself.																																																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.81

### Advanced Techniques - Only 4 allowed ----------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ability Name			Unique Key					SORTKEY					Category of Ability		Type								Description																																																																																				Source Page
Advanced / Battlecry		KEY:MA_OS ~ Battlecry			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:You may unnerve your opponents. You may use this power once per encounter with a group of enemies. It affects all opponents with 30' and forces them to make a Will saving throw at DC 10 +(Con Mod) or become shaken for 1d6 rounds. This Standard Action does not affect creatures that are higher level than you, non-sentient, deaf, or immune to fear.																											SOURCEPAGE:p.81
Advanced / Blinding Strike	KEY:MA_OS ~ Blinding Strike		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:You may attempt to partially blind or otherwise disorient an opponent on a critical hit. The effect, whether ringing ears, blood in the eyes, or vertigo from a head wound, persists for 2d4 rounds. It imposes a 20%% spell failure chance and a -2 circumstance penalty on attack rolls, AC, and saving throws. It does not affect opponents immune to critical hits or who are two size categories or more larger than you, or who make a Fort save at DC 15 +(Str Mod). The critical hit deals damage as normal.
Advanced / Breaking		KEY:MA_OS ~ Breaking			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:When attempting to destroy objects, you may add your Martial Arts skill to the Strength check.
Advanced / Crippling		KEY:MA_OS ~ Crippling			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:On a critical hit, you may opt to deal 1d4 temporary attribute damage rather than inflict extra injury. Select Dexterity, Strength, or Constitution when you gain this ability, it may be gained multiple times but only once per attribute. It does not affect opponents two or more size categories larger than you.
Advanced / Instant Stand	KEY:MA_OS ~ Instant Stand		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:You may stand up as a Free Action if unarmored or in light armor.
Advanced / Mighty Blow		KEY:MA_OS ~ Mighty Blow			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:On a critical hit, you automatically trip your opponent.
Advanced / Mind Like Moon	KEY:MA_OS ~ Mind Like Moon		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:You reflexively come on guard when attacked. With a DC 15 Reflex save, you avoid being surprised or flat-footed at the beginning of combat.
Advanced / Prone Combat		KEY:MA_OS ~ Prone Combat		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:You take no penalties and opponents gain no bonuses when you lie on the ground.
Advanced / Reach			KEY:MA_OS ~ Reach				SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:You add 5' to your Reach in combat. This usually represents lunging and darting in and out, but could be a mystical ability.
Advanced / Sneak Attack		KEY:MA_OS ~ Sneak Attack		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:Add +1d6, as per a Rogue's ability [unlike many point-buy abilities, this does not affect creatures immune to critical hits]. This may be taken more than once, up to a maximum of +4d6.
Advanced / Versatility		KEY:MA_OS ~ Versatility			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:You may change your damage with the specified martial arts weapon or unarmed attacks from lethal to subdual without penalty, and between bludgeoning, slashing, and piercing.
Advanced / Weapon Kata		KEY:MA_OS ~ Weapon Kata			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_B	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerAdvanced	DESC:The user may employ his or her martial art with a particular weapon [e.g., "Longswords"]. This isn't relevant for dedicated weapon forms (e.g., those based on Weapon Finesse rather than Improved Unarmed Strike), although an "Unarmed Kata" might exist in an advanced weapon form.

# Master and Occult Martial Arts Techniques
Master / Blind-Fight		KEY:MA_OS ~ Blind-Fight			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Blind-Fight feat - In melee, every time you miss because of concealment, you can reroll your miss chance percentile roll one time to see if you actually hit.
Master / Combat Reflexes	KEY:MA_OS ~ Combat Reflexes		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Combat Reflexes feat - You may make a number of additional attacks of opportunity equal to your Dexterity bonus.
Master / Deflect Arrows		KEY:MA_OS ~ Deflect Arrows		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Deflect Arrows feat - Once per round when you would normally be hit with a ranged weapon, you may deflect it so that you take no damage from it.
Master / Dodge			KEY:MA_OS ~ Dodge				SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Dodge feat - During your action, you designate an opponent and receive a +1 dodge bonus to Armor Class against attacks from that opponent.
Master / Expertise		KEY:MA_OS ~ Expertise			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Combet Expertise feat - When you use the attack action or the full attack action in melee, you can take a penalty of as much as %1 on your attack roll and add the same number as a dodge bonus to your Armor Class.|CombatExpertiseMax
Master / Improved Bull Rush	KEY:MA_OS ~ Improved Bull Rush	SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Improved Bull Rush feat - When you perform a bull rush you do not provoke an attack of opportunity from the defender. You also gain a +4 bonus on the opposed Strength check you make to push back the defender.
Master / Improved Disarm	KEY:MA_OS ~ Improved Disarm		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Improved Disarm feat - You do not provoke an attack of opportunity when you attempt to disarm an opponent, nor does the opponent have a chance to disarm you. You also gain a +4 bonus on the opposed attack roll you make to disarm your opponent.
Master / Improved Trip		KEY:MA_OS ~ Improved Trip		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Improved Trip feat - You do not provoke an attack of opportunity when you attempt to trip an opponent while you are unarmed and gain a +4 bonus on your Strength check to trip your opponent. If you trip an opponent in melee combat, you immediately get a melee attack against that opponent.
Master / Mobility			KEY:MA_OS ~ Mobility			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Mobility feat - You get a +4 dodge bonus to Armor Class against attacks of opportunity caused when you move out of or within a threatened area.
Master / Quick Draw		KEY:MA_OS ~ Quick Draw			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Quick Draw feat - You can draw a weapon as a free action instead of as a move action. You can draw a hidden weapon as a move action. A character who has selected this feat may throw weapons at his full normal rate of attacks (much like a character with a bow).
Master / Rapid Shot		KEY:MA_OS ~ Rapid Shot			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Rapid Shot feat - You can get one extra attack per round with a ranged weapon. The attack is at your highest base attack bonus, but each attack you make in that round takes a -2 penalty. You must use the full attack action to use this feat.
Master / Sunder			KEY:MA_OS ~ Sunder			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Improved Sunder feat - When you strike at an object held or carried by an opponent (such as a weapon or shield), you do not provoke an attack of opportunity. You also gain a +4 bonus on any attack roll made to attack an object held or carried by another character.
Master / Whirlwind Attack	KEY:MA_OS ~ Whirlwind Attack		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_C	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerMaster	DESC:As Whirlwind feat - When you use the full attack action, you can give up your regular attacks and instead make one melee attack at your full base attack bonus against each opponent within reach.

# Occult Techniques draw upon the user's life energy to surpass the limits of ordinary physical skill. They're extraordinary abilities that drain Con points to use (the cost for each is listed after its name). A martial art may include up to four such abilities, starting at skill level 11.
Occult / Focused Blow		KEY:MA_OS ~ Focused Blow		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-2 Con) You may combine all your attacks against a single target into a single mighty blow made with your highest attack bonus. For example, if you normally attacked at +12/+7/+2, a focused blow would cause triple damage at +12.
Occult / Healing Hand		KEY:MA_OS ~ Healing Hand		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-3 Con) Your touch does any one of the following: (1) Cures 3d6 damage. (2) Cures 2 points of temporary attribute damage. (3) Provides a +8 bonus on a save versus a disease or toxin. The target gets an additional save if you use this.
Occult / Inner Strength		KEY:MA_OS ~ Inner Strength		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:You gain six phantom Con points with which to power your Occult Techniques. These do not add to your hit points. This can be taken twice. Phantom points regenerate like normal Con points.
Occult / Iron Skin		KEY:MA_OS ~ Iron Skin			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-2 Con) You gain +4 natural armor for 1d6 minutes. This is fully effective against ghosts or other intangible creatures, and allows you to make physical contact with such entities.
Occult / Ki Block			KEY:MA_OS ~ Ki Block			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-2 Con) You may make a DC 20 Reflex check to block or dodge a single successful melee attack OR may make a second save (DC 15) against any attack which normally allows a Reflex save. If either save succeeds the effect is normal for a successful save. If both do the effect is entirely negated.
Occult / Ki Focus			KEY:MA_OS ~ Ki Focus			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-1 Con) You may grant yourself a +4 Sacred or Profane (choose when this ability is taken) bonus on the effective value of a skill or attribute for 1d6 minutes.
Occult / Light Foot		KEY:MA_OS ~ Light Foot			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-2 Con) You gain +20' movement and takes half damage from falls for 1d6 minutes. You may expend a single Con point at any time to power an incredible leap (+30 bonus) or a very brief run across an unsuitable surface (such as water or grease).
Occult / One Finger		KEY:MA_OS ~ One Finger			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-1 Con) You may launch a single melee attack at a range of up to 60'. It remains a melee attack but is treated as force damage. When using a weapon form, your weapon either returns or is merely the focus for your attack; you don't have to go and get it back.
Occult / Overburden		KEY:MA_OS ~ Overburden			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-3 Con) This allows you to render one enemy you hit unconscious this round unless he or she makes a Will save at DC 10 +(Wis Mod).
Occult / Paralyze			KEY:MA_OS ~ Paralyze			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-2 Con) This allows you to paralyze any one enemy you hit this round for 1d6 minutes unless he or she makes a Fortitude save at DC 10 +(Wis Mod).
Occult / Resist Pain		KEY:MA_OS ~ Resist Pain			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-2 Con) You gain Damage Reduction 4/- and the ability to remain conscious and functioning up until the point of actual death, for 1d6 minutes. Any effect that relies on pain or Stun effects fail against you this period. This stacks with the basic Toughness ability.
Occult / Serpent Strike		KEY:MA_OS ~ Serpent Strike		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-3 Con) Serpent Strike allows you to create dangerous imbalances in opponents' life essences. This allows you to deal 2d4 attribute damage to any one attribute with one attack this round. if the target fails his or her Fort save at DC 10 +(Wis Mod).
Occult / Touch Strike		KEY:MA_OS ~ Touch Strike		SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-1 Con) One attack you make this round is a touch attack.
Occult / Vanishing		KEY:MA_OS ~ Vanishing			SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-4 Con) You may use a momentary burst of incredible speed, taking an instant one-round Move Action as if you had cast a Timestop spell.
Occult / Wrath			KEY:MA_OS ~ Wrath				SORTKEY:Martial_Arts_Display_D	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MartialArtsOutput.MASkillTrackerOccult	DESC:(-2 Con) Your martial blows inflict energy damage, rather than physical damage, for 3d6 rounds. You must select an energy form when taking this technique. You also gain resistance 12 to that energy type for the duration.

